OL,3,CPM will 'look into' changing Mental
OL,4,CCapacity Act after murder of autistic
OL,5,Cman
OL,7,FThe Prime Minister has been urged to
OL,8,Fchange the law on mental capacity
OL,9,Fassessments, following the murder of
OL,10,Fan autistic man in his own home, as
OL,11,FITV News Political Correspondent
OL,12,FRomilly Weeks reports
OL,14,FThe prime minister has confirmed he'll
OL,15,F"certainly look into" a law change to
OL,16,Fthe way mental capacity assessments
OL,17,Fare carried out, after ITV News
OL,18,Frevealed some vulnerable adults are
OL,19,Fnot getting the support they urgently
OL,20,Fneed.
