OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer was asked at Prime
OL,8,FMinister's Questions about the case of
OL,9,F24-year-old Christopher Laskaris, an
OL,10,Fautistic man who was exploited and
OL,11,Fultimately murdered in his own home by
OL,12,Fa convicted criminal.
OL,14,FDespite years of his mother Fiona
OL,15,Fpleading for help for her vulnerable
OL,16,Fadult son, he was never given a mental
OL,17,Fcapacity assessment to determine the
OL,18,Fhelp he desperately needed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
