OL,7,FMPs from all three main political
OL,8,Fparties are now urging the government
OL,9,Fto make a key change to the new Mental
OL,10,FHealth Bill that would ensure the
OL,11,Fviews of family members are taken into
OL,12,Faccount when deciding whether an adult
OL,13,Fneeds a mental capacity assessment.
